\"><span class=\"fn\">e₁</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/Equiv/Defs.html#Equiv.symm\">symm</a></span></span>) <span class=\"fn\">a✝</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Logic/Equiv/Defs.html#Equiv.arrowCongr_apply","kind":"theorem","line":448,"name":"Equiv.arrowCongr_apply","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/8f9d9cff6bd728b17a24e163c9402775d9e6a365/Mathlib/Logic/Equiv/Defs.lean#L448-L448"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/Equiv/Defs.html#Equiv.arrowCongr\"><span class=\"name\">Equiv</span>.<span class=\"name\">arrowCongr</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α₁</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Sort</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β₁</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Sort</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α₂</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Sort</a> u_3}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β₂</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Sort</a> u_4}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\">α₁</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/Equiv/Defs.html#Equiv\">≃</a> <span class=\"fn\">α₂</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e₂</span> : <span class=\"fn\">β₁</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/Equiv/Defs.html#Equiv\">≃</a> <span class=\"fn\">β₂</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α₁</span> → <span class=\"fn\">β₁</span>)</spa